OL,6,CG1980FJan Leeming is the duty news
OL,7,Fpresenter on Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,8,
OL,9,FNews breaks that the SAS stormed the
OL,10,FIranian Embassy. Jan presents a
OL,11,FNewsflash (BBC Two), breaking into
OL,12,Fsnooker coverage. Kate Adie is the main
OL,13,Freporter at the scene.
OL,14,
OL,15,FIt is the longest Newsflash ever
OL,16,Fcarried on BBC One/BBC Two.
